100","transliteration":"man"},{"id":"ac-80:8:3","surahNum":80,"ayahNum":8,"wordNum":3,"arabic":"جاءَ","targetTranslation":"he came to you","ayahArabic":"وَأَمَّا مَن جَآءَكَ يَسْعَىٰ","ayahEnglish":"But as for he who came to you striving [for knowledge]","blankPosition":-1,"distractors":["he increased","he forbade","he purified"],"pos":"V","lemma":"جاءَ","tier":"q100","transliteration":"jāaka"},{"id":"ac-80:8:4","surahNum":80,"ayahNum":8,"wordNum":4,"arabic":"سَعَى","targetTranslation":"he moves quickly/strives (in this ayah, describing someone coming eagerly)","ayahArabic":"وَأَمَّا مَن جَآءَكَ يَسْعَىٰ","ayahEnglish":"But as for he who came to you striving [for knowledge]","blankPosition":-1,"distractors":["endeavored","attempted","struggled"],"pos":"V","lemma":"سَعَى","tier":"q600","transliteration":"yasʿā"},{"id":"ac-80:9:2","surahNum":80,"ayahNum":9,"wordNum":2,"arabic":"خَشِيَ","targetTranslation":"he is afraid (of what comes next in the ayah)","ayahArabic":"وَهُوَ يَخْشَىٰ","ayahEnglish":"While he fears [Allāh],","blankPosition":-1,"distractors":["he loved","he hoped","he denied"],"pos":"V","lemma":"خَشِيَ","tier":"q300","transliteration":"yakhshā"},{"id":"ac-80:10:3","surahNum":80,"ayahNum":10,"wordNum":3,"arabic":"تَلَهَّى","targetTranslation":"he deliberately busied himself (with عَنْهُ - away from it)","ayahArabic":"فَأَنتَ عَنْهُ تَلَهَّىٰ","ayahEnglish":"From him you are distracted.","blankPosition":-1,"distractors":["Said","comes","he fell down"],"pos":"V","lemma":"تَلَهَّى","tier":"q_all","transliteration":"talahhā"},{"id":"ac-80:11:3","surahNum":80,"ayahNum":11,"wordNum":3,"arabic":"تَذْكِرَة","targetTranslation":"a reminder (general/any reminder)","ayahArabic":"كَلَّآ إِنَّهَا تَذْكِرَةٌ","ayahEnglish":"No! Indeed, they [i.e., these verses] are a reminder;","blankPosition":-1,"distractors":["a recollection","a memorandum","a remembrance"],"pos":"N","lemma":"تَذْكِرَة","tier":"q1000","transliteration":"tadhkiratun"},{"id":"ac-80:12:2","surahNum":8