d [i.e., cursed] is man; how disbelieving is he.","blankPosition":-1,"distractors":["when","where","who"],"pos":"N","lemma":"ما","tier":"q100","transliteration":"mā"},{"id":"ac-80:17:4","surahNum":80,"ayahNum":17,"wordNum":4,"arabic":"أَكْفَرَ","targetTranslation":"made him reject/disbelieve","ayahArabic":"قُتِلَ ٱلْإِنسٰنُ مَآ أَكْفَرَهُۥ","ayahEnglish":"Destroyed [i.e., cursed] is man; how disbelieving is he.","blankPosition":-1,"distractors":["befalls him","He has sent it down","will make him immortal"],"pos":"V","lemma":"أَكْفَرَ","tier":"q_all","transliteration":"akfarahu"},{"id":"ac-80:18:2","surahNum":80,"ayahNum":18,"wordNum":2,"arabic":"أَيّ","targetTranslation":"from what kind (of شَىْءٍ did He create it)","ayahArabic":"مِنْ أَىِّ شَىْءٍ خَلَقَهُۥ","ayahEnglish":"From what thing [i.e., substance] did He create him?","blankPosition":-1,"distractors":["punishment","gardens","messenger"],"pos":"N","lemma":"أَيّ","tier":"q100","transliteration":"ayyi"},{"id":"ac-80:18:3","surahNum":80,"ayahNum":18,"wordNum":3,"arabic":"شَىْء","targetTranslation":"any thing (possessed by أَيِّ)","ayahArabic":"مِنْ أَىِّ شَىْءٍ خَلَقَهُۥ","ayahEnglish":"From what thing [i.e., substance] did He create him?","blankPosition":-1,"distractors":["fruit","book","sign"],"pos":"N","lemma":"شَىْء","tier":"q100","transliteration":"shayin"},{"id":"ac-80:18:4","surahNum":80,"ayahNum":18,"wordNum":4,"arabic":"خَلَقَ","targetTranslation":"he created him (referring to man in أَىِّ شَىْءٍ)","ayahArabic":"مِنْ أَىِّ شَىْءٍ خَلَقَهُۥ","ayahEnglish":"From what thing [i.e., substance] did He create him?","blankPosition":-1,"distractors":["He judged","He forbade","He increased"],"pos":"V","lemma":"خَلَقَ","tier":"q100","transliteration":"khalaqahu"},{"id":"ac-80:19:2","surahNum":80,"ayahNum":19,"wordNum":2,"arabic":"نُطْفَة","targetTranslation":"from a tiny drop (of special fluid that creates babies)","ayahArabic":"مِن نُّطْفَةٍ خَلَقَهُۥ فَقَدَّرَهُۥ","ayahEnglish":"From a sperm-drop He created him